Rebekah Staton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rebekah_Staton 0 Rebekah Staton (born 17 June 1981 in Leek, Staffordshire, England) is an English actress. She is best known for narrating Don't Tell The Bride and appearing as Della in Raised by Wolves. She has also appeared in numerous other British TV programmes like DanTDM Creates a Big Scene as a voice actress.
